{"tid":907277,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：遲早用機械人做領隊","createTime":"2018-11-18T16:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T09:48:47.000Z","uid":1121,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9c21660a9c192cf0c316fe5c4cf173fb858cee","tid":907277,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=vaYKX5YmjG5s9hU83Vc5zcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=15388d81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】受盡長時間批評的前阿仙奴領隊雲加看來對網絡世代感到心灰意冷，直言以機械人代替領隊的日子不在遠矣。<br />\n<br />\n69歲的雲加（Arsene Wenger）在執教阿仙奴的最後一段日子飽受批評，更有不少負面聲音來自網民。這種「網絡民粹」似已令雲加非常氣餒：「你可以想像不久將來會有球會主席公然稱，在球賽中用社交網絡的票選方式去決定如何換人。這就有如民主社會一樣，成為小數派決定一切的霸權。你更可以幻想20年之後，一位機械人會代替領隊坐在你的眼前。」<br />\n<br />\n這種由機械人代替領隊分析球隊數據，然後作出各種球會決策的想法雖然有點妙想天開，但並非絕無可能。只是這位法籍名帥明言，他對此並不認同：「這種想法越來越多人支持，我認為總有一天會發生。只是個人而言我絕不會接受，因為我是接受舊一套訓練模式的人。」"},{"pid":"6f24102c899a46fd72cda1f6cca615e905d9be98","tid":907277,"uid":1121,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Djffhz4W4AANucU.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDjffhz4W4AANucU.jpg%3Alarge&h=7bdaf6b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6911254547d399806f259439707dd4e71d047fd","tid":907277,"uid":64181,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/76a6fcbb76904c83fc3e58d82cf1f145/tumblr_p2d0dwp0mk1vvwgg7o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F76a6fcbb76904c83fc3e58d82cf1f145%2Ftumblr_p2d0dwp0mk1vvwgg7o1_500.gif&h=5a78df83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d6660fd51eeaa2077a4131e47b5c6f279930ee8","tid":907277,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":36,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:22:40.000Z","msg":"機械雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 